at's past the three kings. You'll eventually get to the coast, but beaches were never really my thing. Oh and a word of warning, I would not continue West on One Eye's path. That will take you straight to the territory of the Black Council. They aren't exactly as terrifying as they make themselves out to be, but they are ambitious and utterly without morals, so they seem like a bunch of pretentious assholes to me. <br /></span></p>\n<p> </p>","folder":"syTU6LfeSHtWgKYt","sort":0,"permission":{"default":2,"vmPmArlBOnlDRCNW":3},"flags":{}}
